      <title>贸易担忧导致台积电和东京电子领跌亚洲科技股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/asian-tech-selloff-deepens-on-worry-over-us-trade-restrictions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美国可能加强对华半导体销售限制，亚洲科技股连续第二天下跌。]]></description>
