    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁 Charoen 的 ThaiBev 将退出 Frasers 地产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/thai-billionaire-s-thaibev-to-exit-stake-in-frasers-property</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国首富苏明哲（Charoen Sirivadhanabhakdi）正寻求按照更清晰的路线重组其庞大的商业帝国，他所创立的饮料巨头将退出他控制的一家房地产公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/thai-billionaire-s-thaibev-to-exit-stake-in-frasers-property</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 00:52:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前官员称日本央行本月可能不会加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/boj-likely-to-skip-rate-hike-this-month-former-executive-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行一位前执行董事表示，日本央行本月不太可能加息，而是将略微削减债券购买规模，以避免加剧日元疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/boj-likely-to-skip-rate-hike-this-month-former-executive-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 00:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
